{"word":"G5545 - χρῖσμα - chrîsma - khris'-mah - Anointing","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">χρῖσμα</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>chrîsma"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>khris'-mah"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Anointing"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"அபிஷேகம் - பால் வேறுபாடற்ற பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"anything smeared on, unguent, ointment, Anointing"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Neuter / பெயர்ச்சொல் (அஃறிணை)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G5548 - χρίω - chríō - khree'-o/5548\">G5548</a>; an <i>unguent</i> or <i>smearing</i>, that is, (figuratively) the special <i>endowment</i> (&ldquo;chrism&rdquo;) of the Holy Spirit: - anointing, unction."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G500 - ἀντίχριστος - antíchristos - an-tee'-khris-tos/500\">G500</a>, <a href=\"#/G5545 - χρῖσμα - chrîsma - khris'-mah/5545\">G5545</a>, <a href=\"#/G5546 - Χριστιανός - Christianós - khris-tee-an-os'/5546\">G5546</a>, <a href=\"#/G5547 - Χριστός - Christós - khris-tos'/5547\">G5547</a>, <a href=\"#/G5548 - χρίω - chríō - khree'-o/5548\">G5548</a>, <a href=\"#/G5580 - ψευδόχριστος - pseudóchristos - psyoo-dokh'-ris-tos/5580\">G5580</a>"}]}